name: Ring Of Ouroboros
description:
You are a pharaoh looking for the lost Ring of Ourboros ! You have ten lives!! And only up to go! Good luck, trying to get the Ring! For if you fail, you die!!

Use the Arrow Keys, or A & D To move, and get your way to the top!

 

Can you beat my high score!!?

Music was Auto Generated by an AI at

http://computoser.com/
